    "As AI progresses, the types of adversarial challenges will shift, highlighting the need for continuous vigilance and innovation.",
    "This landscape necessitates a focus on robust defences, ethical AI security norms, and the widereaching implications of adversarial AI for cybersecurity and individual privacy.The paper began by delving into the profound implications of AI-driven cyberattacks, highlighting their surge in prevalence and sophistication.",
